              "><div class="flex justify-center items-end"><span class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#FF1033]">200</span><span class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#FF1033] ml-1">+</span></div><p class="mt-2 text-xl font-medium text-gray-900">Employees</p></div></div></div></section><section class="bg-[#FFF1D9] py-24 relative overflow-hidden"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto  text-center"><div class="px-6 md:px-20"><p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-gray-700">TESTIMONIALS</p><h2 class="mt-3 text-4xl  font-semibold text-gray-900">What our clients are saying?</h2><p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><div>Discover what our clients say about our seamless services and expert support.<br/></div><div> Their success is our pride.</div></p><div class="mt-8"><a class="bg-[#FF1033] flex w-max mx-auto gap-2 items-center text-[#FFFDF5] px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-[#511313] hover:text-[#FF1033] transition-all duration-300" href="https://search.google.com/local/writereview?placeid=ChIJodMavDbjDDkR1TtffPiCv1s">Reviews us on<!-- --> <img width="20" height="20" src="/google.webp" alt=""/></a></div></div><div class="relative w-full"><div class="relative mt-20 px-6 md:px-20 overflow-hidden"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(100px)"><div class=" bg-[#FFFCF6] rounded-2xl p-8 text-left flex flex-col justify-between"><p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">DU GLOBAL provided outstanding guidance and demonstrated thorough understanding of our business requirements. Their expertise in the matter and their professional approach are highly commendable. They collaborate closely and offer tailored advice that perfectly suits our needs. Thanks to their direction as we have optimized operations, boosted productivity and attained growth.</p><div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-8"><span class="inline-block lazy-load-image-background blur" style="color:transparent;display:inline-block"><sp